article.headline: Florida A&M 62, Morgan St. 59
article.story: BALTIMORE (AP) -- Rome Sanders scored a game-high 26 points and grabbed 7 rebounds, and Florida A&M defeated Morgan State 62-59 Wednesday night. Brian Greene added 14 points for Florida A&M (7-7) and grabbed a team-high eight rebounds. Jamar Smith scored a team-high 22 points for Morgan (2-9). Ronald Timus grabbed a game-high nine rebounds for the Bears.
